T02TD2310E:250a-0: @250a * // rig byed mkhan la gdams pa bzhugs//
T02TD2310E:250a-2: # // dpal ldan thugs kyi gsang ba nas //
T02TD2310E:250a-3: rin chen sgron gyi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD2310E:250a-4: log rtog mun pa sel mdzad pas //
T02TD2310E:250a-5: blo yi legs spyad bsam par rigs //
T02TD2310E:250a-6: sngon sbyangs bskal pa mang po nas //
T02TD2310E:250a-7: rgyal ba mnyes byed dge ba bskrun //
T02TD2310E:250a-8: don dam pa yi rang bzhin ni //
T02TD2310E:250a-9: shes rab mchog ldan de la gsal //
T02TD2310E:250a-10: ye shes sgyu 'dra'i rgyal ba dang //
T02TD2310E:250a-11: log rtog sgyu 'dra'i sems can yang //
T02TD2310E:250a-12: sgyu ma yin phyir rang bzhin mnyam //
T02TD2310E:250a-13: de ltar yongs shes 'gal ba med //
T02TD2310E:250a-14: shes rab chos skur tshul gcig cing //
T02TD2310E:250a-15: thabs rnams gzugs skur tshul gcig pa //
T02TD2310E:250a-16: dbyer med dpyad du med pas na //
T02TD2310E:250a-17: sems las sangs rgyas nges par bya //
T02TD2310E:250a-18: de lta bas na bsgrub bya'i lam med cing //
T02TD2310E:250b-0: 'bad pa byas pa don med @250b gyen zhig / dper na dgra med skyes bu zhig / rang gi grib mas 'jigs pa ltar //
T02TD2310E:250b-1: brtabs pa'i 'khrul blo can la ni //
T02TD2310E:250b-2: snying rje skye bar cis mi rigs //
T02TD2310E:250b-3: snying rje sgyu ma lta bu yis //
T02TD2310E:250b-4: thabs kyi spyod ba cir yang ston //
T02TD2310E:250b-5: 'khor ba spong bar mi byed cing //
T02TD2310E:250b-6: thar la 'dod pa mi bskyed kyang //
T02TD2310E:250b-7: rang bzhin shes rab chen po yis //
T02TD2310E:250b-8: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa de ltar bsgoms //
T02TD2310E:250b-9: chos rnams rang bzhin shes pa yis //
T02TD2310E:250b-10: rnam dag sems kyi dbyings la rol //
T02TD2310E:250b-11: ngo bo stong pas rtag dang bral //
T02TD2310E:250b-12: rang bzhin bde bas chad pa med //
T02TD2310E:250b-13: ma bcos gzod nas rnam par dag / dbyer med zung 'jug sngags kyi lam //
T02TD2310E:250b-14: gnyis med spros dang bral ba'i phyir //
T02TD2310E:250b-15: ming tsam du yang mi dmigs so //
T02TD2310E:250b-16: rmi lam skyes bus dug 'thungs ltar //
T02TD2310E:250b-17: srid las nyon mongs de ltar shes //
T02TD2310E:250b-18: dug gi sdug bsngal mi bzad pa //
T02TD2310E:250b-19: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal de tsam mo //
T02TD2310E:250b-20: rmi lam du yang nad bsal ltar //
T02TD2310E:250b-21: lam gyi rig pa de bzhin no //
T02TD2310E:250b-22: de nyid 'bras bu mi bslu bas //
T02TD2310E:250b-23: ma rig gnyid log rnams la nges //
T02TD2310E:250b-24: 'khor ba rmi lam ltar shes pas //
T02TD2310E:250b-25: mi 'gyur bde thob rlom sems med //
T02TD2310E:250b-26: mtshan ma'i log rtog bral ba na //
T02TD2310E:250b-27: ye shes chen po chos kyi sku //
T02TD2310E:250b-28: bsod nams rgyal ba'i gzugs sku la //
T02TD2310E:250b-29: ting 'dzin dpe byad dag gis spras //
T02TD2310E:250b-30: rnam smin lus la tshul bzhin du //
T02TD2310E:250b-31: sku gsung 'byor pa 'bras bu'i mchog / rnal 'byor shes rab ting 'dzin gyis //
T02TD2310E:250b-32: sems can thub pa'i spyod yul spyod //
T02TD2310E:250b-33: gnas med dmigs pa'i rdul dang bral //
T02TD2310E:250b-34: sems can khams la skye ba med //
T02TD2310E:250b-35: de ltar shes ba'i rnal 'byor la //
T02TD2310E:250b-36: mi bya ci yang yod ma yin //
T02TD2310E:250b-37: lus kyi spyod pa la sogs med //
T02TD2310E:250b-38: nam mkha'i ri mo bzhin du blta //
T02TD2310E:250b-39: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba ste //
T02TD2310E:250b-40: sems dang sems snang tsam du 'dus //
T02TD2310E:250b-41: sems kyi rang bzhin byang chub la //
T02TD2310E:250b-42: byang chub kyang ni sems nyid do //
T02TD2310E:250b-43: de ltar sems kyi rang bzhin de //
T02TD2310E:250b-44: nyan thos gang zag med par shes //
T02TD2310E:250b-45: rang rgyal zung don med par shes //
T02TD2310E:250b-47: dbu mas don dam bden pa la //
T02TD2310E:251a-0: sngags kyi bden pa dbyer med @251a * //
T02TD2310E:251a-2: snang ba'i bag chags che chung gis //
T02TD2310E:251a-3: theg pa'i dbye ba bsam mi khyab //
T02TD2310E:251a-4: rgyu la ma brtan 'bras bu ni //
T02TD2310E:251a-5: med ces thub pas mdo ru gsungs //
T02TD2310E:251a-6: rgyu med 'bras bur dag pa ni //
T02TD2310E:251a-7: khyod kyi yul min bden pa'i bka' //
T02TD2310E:251a-8: chos rnams rnam par sgrub byed cing //
T02TD2310E:251a-9: mtshan nyid tsam du dmigs pa na //
T02TD2310E:251a-10: rigs pas gnod pa la sogs pa //
T02TD2310E:251a-11: dngos por lta rnams phan tshun gsal //
T02TD2310E:251a-12: de ltar rnam par dpyad pa yis //
T02TD2310E:251a-13: phyag rgya chen po'i tshul la ni //
T02TD2310E:251a-14: phyogs tsam reg pa ma yin pas //
T02TD2310E:251a-15: rgya mtsho chen po mjal dang mtshungs//
T02TD2310E:251a-16: phyi nang snang srid chos rnams kun //
T02TD2310E:251a-17: rang bzhin gnyis med gdod nas dag / lam gyis bcos nas bsgrub tu med //
T02TD2310E:251a-18: rtsol med lhun gyis grub pa'o //
T02TD2310E:251a-19: gser gyi gling na rdo rje med ltar //
T02TD2310E:251a-20: phyi nang bsdus pa'i chos rnams la //
T02TD2310E:251a-21: skyon zhes ming yang ma grub ste //
T02TD2310E:251a-22: thams cad rol pa'i rgyan du 'gyur //
T02TD2310E:251a-23: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug tilli pas //
T02TD2310E:251a-24: grong khyer padma can gyi rig byed mkhan la gdams pa sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya ba ai thi//
